## Overview

This dashboard provides visualizations for Threat and User from the Symantec Endpoint Security Integration.

The dashboard breaks down User Session Event by Authentication Protocol, Events by Threat, User by Cloud resource UID and User by Domain. It highlights the Top 10 Event by User, Top 10 Vulnerability Details and Top 10 Threat Name by Risk Rating.
